high_descs: Walk forward to the coffee table, walk between the coffee table and the couch, then turn left to face the coffee table.
Pick up the newspaper that is on the coffee table.
Turn around completely to face the couch behind you.
Place the newspaper behind the remote control that is on the right.
anns.task_desc: Move a newspaper from the coffee table to the sofa.

high_descs: Proceed to coffee table, turn right, proceed to couch, turn left to go to coffee table.  Face coffee table.
Pick up newspaper from left hand side of coffee table.
Turn around to face couch.
Place newspaper on its side onto couch, diagonally, touching the remote closest to the pillow.
anns.task_desc: Move a newspaper from a table to a couch.

high_descs: Move to the side of the coffee table closest to the couch facing the newspaper
Pick up the newspaper on top of the coffee table
Carry the newspaper and turn around facing the left side of the striped couch
Place the newspaper behind the remote control on the edge of the couch
anns.task_desc: Move a newspaper to the couch

high_descs: Head towards the couch and face the table.
Pick up the newspaper from the table.
Turn around and face the couch.
Set the newspaper down on the couch
anns.task_desc: Put the newspaper on the couch.

high_descs: Walk towards the couch on the left, sit on the white pillow to face the tv.
Pick up the newspaper from the table.
Stand up and turn around.
Place the newspaper towards the top of the closest remote.
anns.task_desc: Place the newspaper next to the remote on the sofa.

high_descs: Walk around the table to the right side of it and face the table.
Pick up the newspaper.
Turn around and face the couch.
Put the newspaper on the couch near the two remote controls.
anns.task_desc: Put a newspaper on the couch.
